WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
The big win isn't AI. The big win is ownership.

00:06.000 --> 00:16.000
A small appliance in your home becomes your private diabetes vault — records, reminders, supplies, questions, care notes, trends, your next appointments.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Not scattered across apps. Not lost in emails. Not forgotten between visits.

00:24.000 --> 00:34.000
Diabetes doesn't only happen at the doctor's office — it happens at breakfast, at bedtime, at the pharmacy, at the kitchen table, at 2 a.m. when something feels off.

00:34.000 --> 00:41.000
So keep the important stuff close — and private. Right in your home.

00:41.000 --> 00:49.000
Close. Private. Ready. That's the edge appliance win.

00:49.000 --> 00:57.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:57.000 --> 01:05.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
